If youy meet this kind of problem https://i.imgur.com/PXRXhWK.png you will need to do the following things:

- go to "C:\Users\r2d2\AppData\Roaming\NuGet"
- replace the content of NuGet.Config with:

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<configuration>
  <packageSources>
    <add key="nuget.org" value="https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json" protocolVersion="3" />
  </packageSources>
</configuration>

-ENJOY
